The following post uses an Engage tactic (bring up a related but relevant topic):
@Britain_People @the_beeguy @ChrisGPackham @DaveGoulson @B_Strawbridge @Buzz_dont_tweet This has happened twice here. Two huge swarms of bees wiped out as farmer blithely continued spraying. The chemicals they use on crops are killing everything - including us, eventually. #farming

This tweet brings up the related topic of the impact of chemicals used on crops and their effect on the environment, specifically bees.

